![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/dce171f5-2f80-4078-80c1-ed53cd25e115/E220.jpg)

The Batman has been released! The dust has settled, the smoke has cleared, and the red strobes light are blazing, but how GOOD was it? After much speculation regarding the future of the DCEU is The Batman a step in the right direction? With some calling it the best Batman movie of all time, what does this film do that others don't? Those questions are more will be answered in this in-depth recap and review!  
  
Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

  
